{"name": "qtmodern6", "metadata": {"name": "qtmodern6", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Topic :: Software Development :: User Interfaces"], "home_page": "https://www.github.com/hualayn/qtmodern6", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["PySide6"], "summary": "PySide6 Widgets Modern User Interface", "upload_time": 1735099637}, "documentation": ["# qtmodern6\n\n`qtmodern6` is based on `gmarull/qtmodern`\n\nthe origin program supports `PyQt`, `PySide2`, but not `PySide6`, and no more maintaining\nand i can not find an alternative one for my pyside6 program\nso considered to make a little modification to apply pyside6\n\nthe theme looks like, maybe a little different\n\n```{image} examples/mainwindow.png\n:align: center\n:alt: Example\n:width: 450px\n```\n\nusage is just like the origin\n\n## Installation\n\nThe recommended way to install is by using `pip`, i.e:\n\n```\npip install qtmodern6\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nIn order to use `qtmodern6`, simply apply the style you want to your\napplication and then, create a `ModernWindow` enclosing the window you want to\n*modernize*:\n\n```\nimport qtmodern6.styles\nimport qtmodern6.windows\n\n...\n\napp = QApplication()\nwin = YourWindow()\n\nqtmodern6.styles.dark(app)\nmw = qtmodern6.windows.ModernWindow(win)\nmw.show()\n\n...\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "qtmodern6._utils", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "qtmodern6._utils.resource_path", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "relative_path", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "qtmodern6._utils.QT_VERSION", "type": null, "documentation": ["tuple: Qt version. "]}, {"name": "qtmodern6._utils.PLATFORM", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "qtmodern6", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "qtmodern6.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": ["str: Package version. "]}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "qtmodern6.styles", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "qtmodern6.styles._apply_base_theme", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "app", "type": {"name": "QApplication", "xref": {"fqname": "PySide6.QtWidgets.QApplication", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Apply base theme to the application.\n\nArgs:\n    app (QApplication): QApplication instance."]}, {"name": "qtmodern6.styles.dark", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "app", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Apply Dark Theme to the Qt application instance.\n\nArgs:\n    app (QApplication): QApplication instance."]}, {"name": "qtmodern6.styles.light", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "app", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Apply Light Theme to the Qt application instance.\n\nArgs:\n    app (QApplication): QApplication instance."]}], "variables": [{"name": "qtmodern6.styles._STYLESHEET", "type": null, "documentation": ["str: Main stylesheet. "]}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "qtmodern6.windows", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "qtmodern6.windows._FL_STYLESHEET", "type": null, "documentation": ["str: Frameless window stylesheet. "]}], "classes": [{"name": "qtmodern6.windows.WindowDragger", "bases": ["QWidget"], "methods": [{"name": "qtmodern6.windows.WindowDragger.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "window", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "parent", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "qtmodern6.windows.WindowDragger.mousePressEvent", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"n